               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-227vb)
 I-1) Maggābit (fols. 2ra-37vc)
 I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     38ra-67rc)
 I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 67va-104rc)
 I-4) Sane (fols.
                     104va-141rc)
 I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 141ra-189rb) 
 I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     190ra-221rc) 
 I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 221va-228ra)
 - Za-ʾaqrabku
                     māḥleta… “The song I am offering…” (concluding prayer) (fol. 228ra) 
 The
                     commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns 
 
 Addition
                     1.</summary>
