               <provenance>Walda Krǝstos is mentioned as the
                     commissioner on 227vb, and in the supplication
                     formulas. Other individuals are mentioned in the supplication formulas: Takla
                     ʾƎgziʾǝnä (e.g., 7vb, 39ra), ʾƎdä Krǝstos (e.g.,
                        45ra, 68rc), ʾƎsṭifānos (e.g., 56rb, 69va), ʾƎdna (e.g., 82rb, 82va), ʾƎlleni (e.g., 64ra,
                     83vb, 84rb), Ṣǝge Gannat (38va), Ṣǝge Dǝngǝl
                        (80rb).</provenance></history>
